{
  "texts": [
    "80% of the text excerpts were used as training data and 20% as testing data.",
    "As an optimizer, the Adam Optimizer method was employed, while the optimization criterion was the Cross-Entropy Loss 56.",
    "The model was trained for 10 epochs with a learning rate of 10 -5, resulting in an accuracy score of 0.85.",
    "Considering that the training data used for each SDG are not of the same size and the fact that a text excerpt is most probably linked to more than one SDG, the accuracy score is acceptable.",
    "In other words, the algorithm effectively answers the question 'how probable is the X policy document to be related to the Y SDG'."
  ]
}